# Shopapi
Api da plataforma Shopapi
#### Steps to run on Dev Mode

  - Clone this repository
  - Download and Install the [Hasura CLI](https://hasura.io/docs/1.0/graphql/core/hasura-cli/index.html)
  - Run The commands:
  - `docker-compose --env-file .env.example up -d`
  - `cd graphql-engine`
  - `hasura migrate apply --endpoint http://localhost:8080`
  - `hasura metadata apply --endpoint http://localhost:8080`
  - Now grapghql server is ready on `http://localhost:8080/v1/graphql`
